<a class="http" href="http://www.newsmth.net/bbscon.php?bid=460&amp;id=282515&amp;ftype=11" style="color:rgb(4,115,7); border-top-width:0px; border-right-width:0px; border-bottom-width:0px; border-left-width:0px; border-style:initial; border-color:initial">http://www.newsmth.net/bbscon.php?bid=460&amp;id=282515&amp;ftype=11</a><span class="anchor" id="line-204"></span></p>
